Legal Calculus Field Guide

This Field Guide is designed as a quick-reference and practical companion to the full Legal Calculus curriculum. It offers distilled insights, module summaries, and procedural tools for self-represented litigants, legal educators, and justice-focused practitioners navigating procedural lawfare, access-to-court issues, and filing strategy.

